title: We Present The Children's Books We Wrote Today!
description: We decided to take on the challenge of writing a children's book and we had award-winning author, Angela Halgrimson, on to critique what we wrote.  Who had the best children's book according to Angela, Dave, Falen, or Jenny?  And who do you think did the best??
